  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/d11a341b4369df020e4d12f609198fbf.avif?t=1664978065\" width=618 height=334 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dance among embers</strong> - fly, dodge and pickup embers of varying colors as you fly up though the smoke of a blazing bonfire!<br></li><li><strong>Never the same</strong> - the game is ever changing as everything gets generated on the beat. Behold the mesmerizing patterns they create!<br></li><li><strong>Discover the embers</strong> - some embers are dying to meet you as they try to take your light for themselves.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/c40f8f0127ebc7eee66626554526f680.poster.avif?t=1664978065\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/c40f8f0127ebc7eee66626554526f680.webm?t=1664978065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Bursting</strong> - burst to release the stored embers in an explosion of colorful fireworks to rack up your score. Repel the embers around you and give yourself some time to breathe!<br></li><li><strong>Multiply at own risk</strong> - burn brighter by keeping the kin within to grow your power but with great power comes great responsibility!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/67261015ce2ce205b1507dc3e2543b26.poster.avif?t=1664978065\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/67261015ce2ce205b1507dc3e2543b26.webm?t=1664978065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Everburning embers</strong> - gain a random powerup as you can shield yourself from harm or burst infinite to bring your score to new heights!<br></li><li><strong>Leaderboards</strong> - burn your mark to secure your spot on the leaderboard, beware as the whole world will try to come for your crown!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/9928fd811a0e37e33b4ee5448e875dd4.poster.avif?t=1664978065\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/9928fd811a0e37e33b4ee5448e875dd4.webm?t=1664978065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Adaptive music</strong> - listen closely as the music adapts to what is happening on screen. If the drums kick in, you know you're in for the real deal!<br></li><li><strong>Color blind support</strong> - see the game through a different lens as there are several overlay settings for different types of colorblindness making the game more accessible.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/9352950e2d10ab7d50a2237bce8d652a.avif?t=1664978065\" width=618 height=158 /></span><br><br>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/d11a341b4369df020e4d12f609198fbf.avif?t=1664978065\" width=618 height=334 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dance among embers</strong> - fly, dodge and pickup embers of varying colors as you fly up though the smoke of a blazing bonfire!<br></li><li><strong>Never the same</strong> - the game is ever changing as everything gets generated on the beat. Behold the mesmerizing patterns they create!<br></li><li><strong>Discover the embers</strong> - some embers are dying to meet you as they try to take your light for themselves.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/c40f8f0127ebc7eee66626554526f680.poster.avif?t=1664978065\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/c40f8f0127ebc7eee66626554526f680.webm?t=1664978065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Bursting</strong> - burst to release the stored embers in an explosion of colorful fireworks to rack up your score. Repel the embers around you and give yourself some time to breathe!<br></li><li><strong>Multiply at own risk</strong> - burn brighter by keeping the kin within to grow your power but with great power comes great responsibility!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/67261015ce2ce205b1507dc3e2543b26.poster.avif?t=1664978065\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2078530/extras/67261015ce2ce205b1507dc3e2543b26.webm?t=16649780